Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.02,0:00:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in an awfully good mood today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite the vulgar boy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know better, Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.08,0:00:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, what's in the bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Some sweets I bought at the hotel for Moritani yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she'll like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And now a shocking new development in this string of random assaults!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Moritani.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been {\i1}arrested{\i0}?
