Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you {\i1}sure{\i0} you can't tell me what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:27.58,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(144,910)\fad(250,250)\1a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\blur.6\fsp3\fscx112}But You're Not Here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.58,0:02:27.58,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(144,910)\fad(250,250)\shad0\blur0.6\fsp3\fscx112}But You're Not Here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:26.62,Default,,0,53,0,,{\an3}It's just if you don't,\Nthat scary-looking old guy—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:28.12,Default,,0,53,0,,{\an3}his name's Yama—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,will get really mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just bet you're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's order something up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Moritani!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure Moritani's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. They're weak, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can definitely hear her thoughts down this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That right? Well then—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me, Moritani?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Manabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura's here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're there, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Manabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Manabe! Kotoura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Honest! I... I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you two screaming about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not allowed back here, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! We only need a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard her. She was clear this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Moritani! I know the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you were just a bystander!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Moritani!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Moritani!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me, Moritani?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friends? They're pretty incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You two truly redefine "temerarious."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna take you in too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:04:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when I heard Moritani had been arrested,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,my brain kind of shut down, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So of course I had to follow her, for her own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I do appreciate your concern,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but please don't end up like {\i1}them{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mori! Mori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mori! Mori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Hiyori free!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mori! Mori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlawful arrest is disgraceful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mori! Mori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Hiyori! We'll save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mori! Mori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mori! Mori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to join them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So just to make sure I'm clear on this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Moritani was arrested on suspicion of\N committing the random assaults, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The reporters and police at school this morning were all thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}I've {\i1}seen{\i0} the real criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We could try making a desperate attempt to tell the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but now that you've gone and done that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, Muroto?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The detective from school?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Moritani!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oo guyz god arres'ed {\i1}oo{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But man, when I actually thought about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I suddenly realized I hadn't eaten since last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh. But I'm glad to see you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She can say that now, but when she heard you calling for her
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,she started blubbering like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive the tangent, but was it {\i1}really{\i0} okay to let us in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. As long as no one finds out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And anyway, having her friends here'll make it easier for her to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Um. She seems to be in earnest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So Moritani, how did you wind up getting yourself arrested?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that rumor that Kotoura knew who the criminal was?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a friend of mine who started it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to stop her from spreading it any further,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but she just got mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to check all the places she'd be likely to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So you found your injured friend after she'd been attacked,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and they arrested you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But is it really standard procedure to arrest someone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,just for being at the scene of a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but we had a tip-off in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A witness said the suspect was being very belligerent, and had made threats on the victim's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And that liar called herself my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So just for trying to stop the rumors about me, Moritani was falsely accused.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Moritani is not the criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:07:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I know who the real culprit is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? {\i1}What{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you bums are having a pretty interesting conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you {\i1}do{\i0} know somethin' about the perp,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't you fill me in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure about this, Kotoura?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukino, send 'em home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I really {\i1}can{\i0} hear people's thoughts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I don't have the time for kids' games.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up, old-timer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think Kotoura {\i1}wants{\i0} to tell you all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Manabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, how about we test her psychic powers on {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna read my mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, I'm shittin' bricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on. No holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:07:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Um. You'd been having a hard time getting by because your wife wouldn't give you any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hemorrhoids were worsening and using the toilet was agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife refused to wash your poop-stained underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hold it—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And late one night, you came home to find no dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In its place were the divorce papers, already signed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I give up. For the love of mercy, spare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll let Moritani go now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry kiddo, no can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Psychic abilities aren't actually supposed to exist,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,so they're not admissible evidence. Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn straight. And we police got our honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let this magic mind-reading mumbo-jumbo do our job for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}honor{\i0} of the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was that "honor" when you took credit for my mother's talents—and then let her die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,President Mifune.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you blabberin' ab—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a feeling I'd seen you somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The daughter of Mifune Chizuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. The clairvoyant's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But, wait—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Let's be on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mifune Chizuru the clairvoyant was pretty well-known among the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She even assisted in police investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Unofficially, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That bein' why we had no choice but to cut her loose
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,when she was declared a fraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,'Course, I didn't believe in this psychic bullshit anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how those kids can stand to be around that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, time for a {\i1}chat{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! But I got the testimony!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut me some slack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it was my fault Moritani was arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be an idiot. You didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's fairly obvious she's innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll clear her of suspicion soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we search for the criminal after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like we can rely on the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving Moritani in their custody would just break my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuriko, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:11:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be a chance to help Moritani with your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My power... can help?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but if my power can help someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Kotoura.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The ESP Society will do everything it can to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,P-President Mifune.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Count me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Manabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never condone the use of psychic powers
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to track down a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Manabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't spoken to you at all since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Not a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's stubborn, like all fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even Kotoura can sway him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura, finding the criminal is {\i1}not{\i0} your responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's my fault Moritani—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me repeat myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It wasn't your fault{\i0}. Moritani knows that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, what can you hope to do if you faint
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,every time you're even {\i1}close{\i0} to the criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought my heart was going to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't bear to see you like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Manabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still believe this is something I {\i1}must{\i0} do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you just {\i1}love{\i0} taking everything on yourself!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't made any progress since you ran off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So doing whatever I can to help people is wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that the person I'm trying to help is a {\i1}friend{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking this kind of risk isn't noble, it's just {\i1}stupid{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}not{\i0} stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never get through that thick head of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?! Fine, do whatever you damn well want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}will{\i0} do what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And Manabe can do what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you {\i1}were{\i0} pretty harsh back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing we can do about someone who's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find this psycho assaulting people in our town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what are these red dots?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The crime scenes, and the point where you walked past the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at this, it's pretty clear the criminal is based inside city limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This spot here where Kotoura ran into him
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is the busiest place in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd assume the criminal was there picking out his victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If he stays downtown, there'll be no shortage of the high school girls he targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll have his pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably follows them until they reach a less crowded area, and then attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kotoura.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:14:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes! Of course I'm not thinking about Manabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You can head home for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, you don't have anything to do yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You should rest up while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sort of feels like old times again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just you and me at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we got an actual esper when Kotoura showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Manabe and Moritani came along, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun while it lasted, but it could never have lasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what I do, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll neither help you nor condemn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here because I choose to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He probably follows them until they reach a less crowded area, and then attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta get home, fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, calm down! It's me, Tsukino!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I'm sorry about the screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, it was my fault for startling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I just happened to see you while I was out investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how is Moritani doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She's doing real good. Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:55.64,ForTomorrow,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fnResPublica\frz327\frx8\fry358\move(1202,982,1128,982,0,1901)}For\NTomorrow\N(Part 1) \N"Mori!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe {\i1}too{\i0} good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell her that we're going to find the real criminal and prove her innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw my power, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear the criminal's thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah, woah. You high school kids definitely shouldn't be messing with this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've made my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why? You want to show off your abilities?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My powers have always isolated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the people I've met here gave me a chance to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to them, I'm not alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,this time, I want to be the one helping them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I don't really follow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just that I've never had any friends myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How can she be so nonchalant?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But it sounds like they must be good friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. They're more than I deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess, since they seem to have no problem hanging around {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Friendship sure is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's not a bad person. She's just a little blunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't she lonely, having no friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, just let the police handle this, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Moritani!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Moritani!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mori!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so grateful you're unharmed, Miss Hiyori!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alive, Kotoura?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Um. I'm sorry for worrying you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were released because the real culprit struck again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I can't be too happy, since someone else got attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's only natural to feel relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't even get a chance to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We were trying to clear your name by finding the criminal ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's pretty reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, could we keep up the search?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've been wondering,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,where's Manabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh, Manabe is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops! Gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault Kotoura and Manabe split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You know those two will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't get any ideas about taking Manabe for yourself, Moritani!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So Kotoura hasn't picked anything up this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And the attacks have stopped abruptly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible the criminal left town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Tsukino.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Kotoura.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey there. How's it been going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we haven't found a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? No, I meant with Moritani.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're really looking for the criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What did I tell you about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's much too dangerous for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is there even any reason to keep looking for the criminal now that Moritani's been released?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:19:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And don't let any of your friends go near that 2nd Street alleyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've gotten word that the suspect may still be hiding out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Promise me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Tsukino!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she want?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She knows we're looking for the criminal,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,so she warned us to stay away from the alleyway off 2nd Street. It's not safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,President Mifune?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't use yourself as bait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my only chance to get back at everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,who sneered at the occult and at my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll all help me, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised it's so crowded at this hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it {\i1}is{\i0} the heart of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:20:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this was the one named Mifune.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So she really {\i1}did{\i0} come.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How does the criminal know President Mifune's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"She really did come"? What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Kotoura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you heard right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Muroto! President Mifune is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Muroto.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You know where the criminal is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so close, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kotoura is a real psychic, just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can finally show the world that you were {\i0}wronged{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.07,0:21:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So just you watch, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.49,0:21:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:22:05.09,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(525,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}How do you stand again when something trips you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:17.94,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,750)\fsp-1.5\blur2}Can truth be found by thinking about the days to come?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.19,0:22:26.19,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(775,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}We all come into this world alone when we are born,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.86,0:22:27.70,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}and precisely because of that,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.36,0:22:34.74,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}we try to live life with others from then on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.62,0:22:43.04,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}Back then you taught me the strength to live and the meaning to it all,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.75,0:22:48.38,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}and I embrace it with all my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.17,0:22:54.93,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}So that in all things around us the flower of hope may bloom,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.64,0:23:00.73,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\fsp-1.5\blur2}we start our days together here
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.85,0:23:07.36,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,525)\fsp-1.5\blur2}We start our days together here
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.71,0:23:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura. I'm done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.59,0:23:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only been a few days! What {\i1}happened{\i0} to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.72,0:23:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't anything sexy in this episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.10,0:23:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems Manabe is suffering from lust withdrawal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.43,0:23:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sadly, there'll be nothing dirty in the next episode either.
